import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'
import Home from './Home'
import Navbar from '../Component/Navbar'

export default function App() {
  return (
   <BrowserRouter>
   <Navbar/>
   <Routes>
    <Route path='/' element={Home}/>
   </Routes>
   </BrowserRouter>
  )
}
